From bd4be76783df2be73d00fc4d1db92304195c8caf Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Yousaf Chaudhry <yousafchaudhry720@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 10 Apr 2026 13:04:14 +0500
Subject: [PATCH] feat: bulk mark status on grid + enhanced reports with
 Excel/PDF export

- Add checkbox column to attendance grid for multi-row selection
- Add Select All / Select by Department controls in grid toolbar
- Show bulk action bar when rows selected: status, empty-only toggle,
  apply-all-period-dates toggle, and Mark Selected button
- Add per-department Auto-fill button in dept separator rows
- New POST /api/attendance/bulk-override route: two-phase upsert
  (updateMany existing + createMany for empty cells, skipDuplicates)
- New GET /api/reports route supporting 8 report types: in-out,
  absentees, dept-summary, dept-summary-regularity, dept-summary-division,
  individual, overtime, attendance
- Rewrite reports-shell.tsx with new filter UI (date range, employee
  multi-select, department, category), client-side Excel export via
  SheetJS, client-side PDF export via jsPDF landscape A4 with company
  header and page numbers
- Install jspdf + jspdf-autotable for PDF generation
- Update reports/page.tsx to fetch active employees and pass to shell

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
